{"tid":626123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港特首幫單程證出聲都唔諗幫本地人先","createTime":"2018-04-12T01:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T10:01:45.000Z","uid":51271,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"18b72f0e22da89eface3ab086b4d03fa4499d54d","tid":626123,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:32:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180412/s00001/1523494168787\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180412%2Fs00001%2F1523494168787&d=Pwj1qcM7NItuKhpa9TTTiqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=0b36bb9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180412%2Fs00001%2F1523494168787&h=84bc27d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180412/s00001/1523494168787</a><br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥昨出席立法會答問時，批評有人說「禁止每日150名持單程證人士到港」便可解決房屋問題，是不切實際、混淆視聽，稱唯有大量開拓土地，才能回應市民期盼。不過一向關注問題的環保觸覺義務總幹事譚凱邦反駁，政府盲目相信土地開發卻不檢討單程證等，才是真正不切實際。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n譚凱邦昨於facebook自言要「對號入座」回應林鄭月娥說法，強調從無人說「單程證」是房屋問題全部，但肯定是極重要成因，認為若不減慢人口遷入，便無法解決「供應追唔上需求增長」問題。<br />\n<br />\n譚凱邦又說，政府多年來單靠「催谷土地開發」，卻未有檢討「單程證」等，「呢啲我諗先係真正不切實際！不知所謂！」他更標籤了「#香港特首幫單程證出聲都唔諗幫本地人先」。"},{"pid":"e5daf70e9c78ab83d4f6f4d7204588412345a6e2","tid":626123,"uid":8048,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:35:59.000Z","msg":"佢會為港豬發聲就奇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd82a544c1b25d4b878988d060dcbfc27b18700","tid":626123,"uid":10637,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:37:22.000Z","msg":"上面order要溝淡你班港英撚"},{"pid":"7107f7578eb417cd15274cdcd3253f195ccc46f1","tid":626123,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:37:31.000Z","msg":"見怪不怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3769a5c3225882c